        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow the child tax credit to be used for stillbirths. A &quot;stillbirth&quot; is delivery after the involuntary death of an unborn child who was carried in the womb for 20 weeks or more.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
